putty If you are having trouble getting solid lines to draw in your putty session, you may need to change the following:
Open putty Go into the configuration screen Click on Window Translation Change Remote character set to UTF-8 You may need to also change Handling of line drawing characters: to Use font in both ANSI and OEM modes
